-for-2025-tour-and-re-sale-prices-will-be-capped-at-face-value-3796216">他们已经宣布将于 2025 年进行“Run For Your Lives”英国和欧洲巡演</a>。请<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-promise-there-will-be-no-dynamic-ticket-pricing-for-2025-tour-and-re-sale-prices-will-be-capped-at-face-value-3796216">在此处</a>查看完整的日期列表并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Firon-maiden-tickets%2Fartist%2F735341" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>查找门票。</p><p> 10月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-iron-maiden-singer-paul-dianno-dies-age-66-what-he-left-behind-will-live-on-forever-3804890">1978年至1981年期间担任乐队主唱的Paul Di&#39;Anno去世，享年66岁</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maidens-nicko-mcbain-to-take-a-step-back-from-the-grind-of-the-extensive-touring-lifestyle-3820013">《铁娘子》乐队成员尼科·麦克贝恩 (Nicko McBain) 的“从繁重的巡演生活方式的苦差事中退一步”的</a>文章首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Charli XCX 和 Gillian Anderson 交换“别致又性感”的话题https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-and-gillian-anderson-exchange-over-being-chic-and-cunty-3820009?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=charli-xcx-and-阿娇安德森交换时尚和小妞Max PilleySat, 07 Dec 2024 16:36:37 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3820009 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor_Hill_VALERIE_MACON.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor_Hill_VALERIE_MACON.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor_Hill_VALERIE_MACON-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor_Hill_VALERIE_MACON-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor_Hill_VALERIE_MACON-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor_Hill_VALERIE_MACON-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor_Hill_VALERIE_MACON-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这段爱情源于《X档案》演员为“励志”《小子》明星写的悼词</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-and-gillian-anderson-exchange-over-being-chic-and-cunty-3820009">Charli XCX 和 Gillian Anderson 就“时尚和性感”交换意见的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor_Hill_VALERIE_MACON.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor_Hill_VALERIE_MACON.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor_Hill_VALERIE_MACON-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor_Hill_VALERIE_MACON-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor_Hill_VALERIE_MACON-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor_Hill_VALERIE_MACON-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor_Hill_VALERIE_MACON-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gillian-anderson">Gillian Anderson</a>一直互相爱着对方，宣称自己“时尚又性感”。</p><p>这次互动源于<i>《X 档案》</i>明星为《<a href="https://www.ft.com/womenof2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>金融时报》</i></a> “2024 年 25 位最具影响力的女性”撰写的致敬文章，其中她将这位《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">小子</a>》明星描述为“灵感”。</p><p>安德森写道：“今年，查莉重新为世界各地的女性重新使用了‘brat’这个词，发行了一张在 12 个国家进入前十名的专辑，用彩绘墙上不断变化的信息吸引了布鲁克林，甚至影响了美国大选。” </p><figure id="attachment_3818863" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3818863" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3818863" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli_xcx_xcx.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli_xcx_xcx.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli_xcx_xcx-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli_xcx_xcx-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli_xcx_xcx-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli_xcx_xcx-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli_xcx_xcx-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3818863" class="wp-caption-text"> Charli XCX 于 2024 年 2 月 3 日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶贝弗利希尔顿酒店。 （莱昂·贝内特/盖蒂图片社为唱片学院拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p> “查理有着清晰的愿景和毫不羞耻的大胆行动。在她反流派的音乐生涯中，她一直回避标签和习俗，转而忠于自己。查莉清楚地了解自己是谁以及自己想要什么，这继续激励着我们所有人。”</p><p> “在一个反叛者可能会让人筋疲力尽的世界里，查莉可以真诚地说，‘我走了自己的路，而且我做到了。’”安德森补充道。 “我迫不及待地想看看她接下来如何运用她的力量。”</p><p>这篇文章传到了查莉本人手中，这位歌手于周五（12 月 6 日）在她的 X 账户上回复了这篇文章，并说道：“吉莉安·安德森，你是如此时尚和狡猾，我爱你”。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">吉莉安·安德森，你是如此的别致和性感，我爱你。 <a href="https://t.co/lYTYfaVBDP">https://t.co/lYTYfaVBDP</a></p><p> — Charli (@charli_xcx) <a href="https://twitter.com/charli_xcx/status/1865157720527065309?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 12 月 6 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>安德森于周六（12 月 7 日）回报了这份爱，在推特上引用了 Charli 的帖子并写道：“永远别致而小气，爱你@charli_xcx”。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">永远别致又小气<br />爱你<a href="https://twitter.com/charli_xcx?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@charli_xcx</a> <a href="https://t.co/U2z547NaKB">https://t.co/U2z547NaKB</a></p><p> -吉莉安·安德森 (@GillianA) <a href="https://twitter.com/GillianA/status/1865368121718018318?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 12 月 7 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> Charli 主导文化的第六张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">Brat</a> 》于六月发行，<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995">并被<i>NME</i>评为年度专辑</a>。 “毫无疑问， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/charli-xcx-brat-summer-timeline-highs-lows-3777880">‘小子’作为一种文化轰动</a>是值得一看的。但《Brat》作为一张专辑——发行时的核心唱片、营销背后的音乐——绝对是独一无二的，” <i>NME</i>指出。</p><p> “作为一名词曲作者和作词家，查理职业生涯的大部分时间都在顽固的态度和赤裸裸的脆弱之间摇摆不定。 《小子》在音阶上毫不费力地移动，给我们带来了坚如磐石的轰动，但仍然具有令人痛苦的人性。这张专辑不仅是 Charli 的巅峰之作，而且为现代流行音乐树立了新的标杆。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/charli-xcx-brat-summer-timeline-highs-lows-3777880">“Brat”夏季</a>演出预计将于 2025 年进行第二轮演出。Charli <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-announced-as-first-parklife-2025-headliner-buy-tickets-3815857">已被确认为明年 Parklife 的首位主角</a>，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-charli-xcxs-star-studded-360-video-with-julia-fox-chloe-sevigny-and-many-more-3755245">“360”</a>艺术家还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-to-headline-and-curate-own-party-girl-festival-at-londons-lido-2025-buy-tickets-3815487">在伦敦 LIDO 音乐节上策划一天的演出，届时她将带来一场超值表演</a>。</p><p>此外，她还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-announces-huge-summer-2025-shows-in-belfast-and-dublin-3814479">在贝尔法斯特和都柏林举办两场户外演出</a>，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2025-lady-gaga-green-day-post-malone-travis-scott-lead-line-up-3814558">2025 年 Coachella</a>音乐节上表演，并在巴塞罗那和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-porto-announce-stacked-2025-line-up-3810606">波尔图</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-says-she-chappell-roan-and-sabrina-carpenter-headlining-primavera-sound-2025-is-the-holy-trinity-3806307">Primavera Sound 上表演</a>。除此之外，她还宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-announces-us-brat-arena-tour-2025-buy-tickets-3815161">将于四月和五月进行美国舞台巡演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-and-gillian-anderson-exchange-over-being-chic-and-cunty-3820009">Charli XCX 和 Gillian Anderson 就“时髦又性感”交换意见的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
